### dispatch_sync任务到其它并发队列中。

```
    dispatch_queue_t queue = dispatch_queue_create("cn.edu.bjtu.myQueue", DISPATCH_QUEUE_CONCURRENT);

    NSLog(@"step0 finished! - %@", [NSThread currentThread]);

    dispatch_sync(queue, ^{     // block1
